node.text: It can be difficult making the right litter choice for your furry baby. @drelseys is the best for so many reasons! The variety of litter options they offer allows you to select the proper litter for your kitty because it does matter! With Dr. Elsey's Ultra litter, every visit to the box is a pleasant experience which keeps me doing my business in the right places. The litter clumps hard with minimal tacking and masks odors which is important since I share my home with 5 kitty siblings. Visit the link in my bio to learn more and make the switch today! #DrElseys #ad

node.text:
Meow! I’m excited to be hosting for @straycatalliance 21st Anniversary Virtual Gala with @NathanTheCatLady next Saturday, September 18th, at 6pm (pst)!

Be sure to get your tickets now at StrayCatClub.org and help us celebrate and raise funds so they can continue their amazing lifesaving work for so many kitties! 

The evening's program will feature entertainment, celebrity guests and cute kittens and cats and ME! Oh, and be sure to check out their fabulous silent auction!

Follow @straycatalliance as they will be sharing more updates! 
Tickets: StrayCatClub.org

node.text: Dressed to impress! The @snapple story is a New York story, built from humble beginnings in the city’s corner stores. Snapple and A$AP Ferg are raising funds to help corner stores that were impacted by the Covid-19 pandemic. 100% of sales from the limited-time only Snapple merch collection will go to The Bodega and Small Business Group. Click the link in my bio to support the cause! #ASnappleCornerStory #ad #SnapplePartner
